---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | GoZeroShot"
  description="Terms of Service for GoZeroShot, including permitted use, user responsibilities, and contact information."
>
  <main class="main legal-page">
    <section class="legal-shell">
      <a class="back-link" href="/">Back to home</a>
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="effective-date">Effective date: March 23, 2026</p>

      <p>
        GoZeroShot is a lightweight content automation service that helps creators
        prepare and publish social media content using connected third-party
        platforms, including TikTok.
      </p>

      <h2>Use of the service</h2>
      <p>
        You may use GoZeroShot only in compliance with applicable laws, platform
        policies, and these terms. You are responsible for the content you upload,
        schedule, or publish through the service.
      </p>

      <h2>Your account</h2>
      <p>
        You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and any
        connected third-party accounts. Do not share credentials with unauthorized
        users. You remain responsible for actions taken through your account.
      </p>

      <h2>Connected platforms</h2>
      <p>
        GoZeroShot may connect to third-party services such as TikTok to enable
        login, profile access, and content publishing. Your use of those services
        remains subject to their own terms and policies.
      </p>

      <h2>Content and permissions</h2>
      <p>
        You retain ownership of the content you submit. By using GoZeroShot, you
        grant the service permission to process, store, and transmit your content
        solely as needed to provide the service features you request.
      </p>

      <h2>Availability</h2>
      <p>
        The service is provided on an &quot;as is&quot; and &quot;as available&quot; basis.
        We may update, suspend, or discontinue features at any time without prior
        notice.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, GoZeroShot is not liable for any
        indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or for
        any loss of data, revenue, profits, or business opportunities arising from
        your use of the service.
      </p>

      <h2>Termination</h2>
      <p>
        We may suspend or terminate access to the service if you violate these
        terms, misuse the service, or create risk for us or third-party platforms.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the service
        after updates take effect means you accept the revised terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms can be sent to
        <a href="mailto:anix@gozeroshot.dev">anix@gozeroshot.dev</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    display: block;
  }

  .legal-shell {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #4a6f98;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  .effective-date {
    color: #6b7280;
  }
</style>
